WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:04.841
<i> Previously on</i> Lucifer...
<i> Someone's escaped from Hell.</i>

00:04.839 --> 00:07.039
Who escaped Hell?
-<i> Mom.</i>

00:07.041 --> 00:08.271
If she's not coming to kill me,

00:08.275 --> 00:10.605
<i> then I don't know</i>
<i> what she's doing.</i>

00:10.611 --> 00:11.741
Aren't you glad
to see me?

00:11.746 --> 00:13.406
I apologize for
my human form.

00:13.414 --> 00:14.484
Chloe, I'm sorry.

00:14.482 --> 00:16.322
You don't get to be sorry.

00:16.317 --> 00:17.447
<i> I've been demoted.</i>

00:17.451 --> 00:18.881
<i> I'm reassigned</i>
<i> to assist on cases.</i>

00:18.886 --> 00:20.946
<i> I need to figure out</i>
<i> where I fit in in this world.</i>

00:20.955 --> 00:22.215
I need some space.

00:22.223 --> 00:24.223
<i> Things have been</i>
<i> very trying for me.</i>

00:24.225 --> 00:25.415
<i> Lucifer made a deal with</i>

00:25.426 --> 00:26.886
your ex to take
you back to Hell.

00:26.894 --> 00:28.394
<i> And he doesn't break deals.</i>

00:28.396 --> 00:30.096
I want what your father
took from me.

00:30.097 --> 00:31.327
All right, you can stay,

00:31.332 --> 00:34.002
just until I figure out
what I need to do.

00:38.973 --> 00:42.373
<i> I want to say I'm sorry...</i>

00:42.376 --> 00:44.406
<i> for all my sins.</i>

00:44.412 --> 00:48.452
For anything I have ever done
that hurt people.

00:48.449 --> 00:51.919
I was stupid.

00:51.919 --> 00:54.919
And I am sorry.

00:54.922 --> 00:58.122
I am so sorry.

01:03.030 --> 01:05.960
All I want now is forgiveness.

01:07.735 --> 01:11.365
I just want to take it all back.

01:11.372 --> 01:12.502
Please.

01:13.541 --> 01:15.111
No! Just let me take it back!

01:15.109 --> 01:18.439
No, no, no, no! No...!

01:26.420 --> 01:28.190
There's no need
for squeals.

01:28.189 --> 01:30.619
We'll stop this torture
any time you like.

01:30.624 --> 01:32.624
Just say the word.

01:32.626 --> 01:34.626
Don't you dare stop.

01:36.797 --> 01:39.927
What happens if he stops?

01:39.934 --> 01:41.704
Well, Lucifer,
don't be shy.

01:41.702 --> 01:43.042
Introduce me
to your friend.

01:43.037 --> 01:44.997
Lucifer,
you brought a surprise.

01:45.005 --> 01:47.165
I most certainly did not bring
any surprises.

01:47.174 --> 01:48.644
Oh, she's beautiful.

01:48.642 --> 01:49.712
That's my mum

01:49.710 --> 01:51.040
you're talking about.

01:54.081 --> 01:56.551
This just got too weird.

02:03.057 --> 02:04.517
Listen, Mum,
I know I chose

02:04.525 --> 02:07.025
not to return you to Hell,
yet...

02:07.027 --> 02:08.487
Which I appreciate.
But that doesn't mean

02:08.496 --> 02:11.726
you can just waltz in here
and accost my guests.

02:11.732 --> 02:13.522
I apologize.

02:13.516 --> 02:15.296
It's just that all
these human rules

02:15.302 --> 02:18.002
and customs are
so confusing.

02:18.005 --> 02:21.105
Remember, I'm still getting
used to this earthly skin sack.

02:21.108 --> 02:23.008
Yes, yes, you used
to be a goddess.

02:23.010 --> 02:24.880
I know, but things
are different now.

02:24.879 --> 02:26.249
And I will figure it out.

02:26.247 --> 02:28.407
Now that we're
together again,

02:28.415 --> 02:30.045
I just want to be
part of your lives.

02:30.050 --> 02:31.680
Not this part!

02:32.520 --> 02:34.390
