02:36.957 --> 02:38.957
Wait. What do you
mean by "lives"?

02:40.027 --> 02:41.687
I want to see Amenadiel.

02:41.695 --> 02:43.955
What?

02:43.964 --> 02:45.934
It's time.

02:45.933 --> 02:48.533
I am not
going to live

02:48.536 --> 02:50.396
in fear of my own son.

02:50.404 --> 02:52.174
We may have had
our differences...

02:52.173 --> 02:54.113
