carried you to Hell.

02:54.108 --> 02:55.438
But I created him.

02:55.442 --> 02:57.612
Certainly that has to
count for something.

02:57.611 --> 02:59.111
It doesn't. Bummer, right?

02:59.113 --> 03:00.283
One look at you,
and he'll take you

03:00.281 --> 03:01.481
right back where you came from.

03:01.482 --> 03:04.582
I'm surprised he hasn't
come sniffing around already.

03:04.585 --> 03:07.245
Well, what am I supposed to do,
just sit here and hide?

03:07.254 --> 03:09.394
See a movie, go to a museum.

03:09.390 --> 03:12.190
Catch up on what's happened over
the past few thousand years.

03:12.193 --> 03:13.933
You'd be surprised.

03:13.928 --> 03:15.128
Yes. I suppose
a lot has changed.

03:15.129 --> 03:16.559
I mean, who would've predicted
you would've

03:16.564 --> 03:18.334
