was the locale.

03:30.978 --> 03:32.378
I know what you're thinking,

03:32.379 --> 03:34.549
but I was assisting on a
stakeout that went long,

03:34.548 --> 03:36.918
and I'm really sorry,
but I promise you,

03:36.917 --> 03:38.677
I will make it
up to you, okay?

03:38.686 --> 03:41.216
How?

03:42.656 --> 03:46.286
Double fudge, your favorite.

03:47.962 --> 03:50.162
You're lucky I like you.

03:54.401 --> 03:55.631
Hey.

03:55.636 --> 03:56.836
Hey.

03:56.837 --> 03:58.967
Thank you for letting me
do the pickup here at work.

03:58.973 --> 04:01.743
I've just been running around
a lot since the demotion.

04:01.742 --> 04:03.182
