04:04.345 --> 04:06.245
Yeah. It's fine, it's fine.

04:06.247 --> 04:08.677
Are we still going
on our family camping trip?

04:08.682 --> 04:11.232
Oh, uh...

04:11.234 --> 04:13.794
We're still ler... working
out the logistics of that.

04:13.787 --> 04:15.787
Of the trip.

04:18.791 --> 04:20.992
Look, I know that
you're still mad at me.

04:20.995 --> 04:22.825
I deserve it.

04:22.830 --> 04:26.160
But this stuff between us is
starting to affect Trixie.

04:26.166 --> 04:28.666
So I think that we
need to talk later.

04:30.371 --> 04:32.601
Yeah, yeah. We should.

04:32.606 --> 04:33.666
You're right.

04:33.674 --> 04:34.914
Uh, Decker.

04:34.908 --> 04:37.608
Okay, yeah.
Two seconds.

04:40.180 --> 04:42.880
<i> I was stupid.</i>

04:42.883 --> 04:44.653
And I'm sorry.

04:46.654 --> 04:48.824
