05:58.659 --> 05:59.689
Smokey Bobinson.

05:59.693 --> 06:00.993
Weekend at Burnie's.

06:00.994 --> 06:02.034
His burning bush?

06:02.029 --> 06:04.199
Oh. Very good.

06:04.198 --> 06:06.198
