You're right, far too subtle.

08:26.773 --> 08:28.943
Why did you torture
the poor young man to death?

08:28.942 --> 08:31.182
Torture him?

08:31.979 --> 08:34.009
Oh, God.

08:34.014 --> 08:36.014
You think I had
something to do with this?

08:36.015 --> 08:37.645
Well, we know about
the angry e-mails.

08:37.650 --> 08:39.051
