09:01.208 --> 09:02.738
There's something
you should see.

09:07.330 --> 09:08.810
Ray, can you come in here,
please?

09:08.815 --> 09:12.145
Ray, I'm gonna need you
to pull up the video

09:12.152 --> 09:14.292
