with interns.

09:27.167 --> 09:29.467
Aka, he could be a real dick.

09:31.104 --> 09:32.374
As you'll see.

09:37.844 --> 09:39.284
Aah! Aah!

09:39.279 --> 09:41.209
My balls! Get it off!

09:46.887 --> 09:48.647
Come on,
that is quite funny.

09:48.655 --> 09:50.555
Nick posted the video
shortly after the retreat,

09:50.557 --> 09:52.987
and even though
it was quickly taken down,

09:52.993 --> 09:54.163
everyone saw it.

09:54.161 --> 09:57.031
Tommy was a
laughingstock.

09:57.030 --> 09:58.430
He quit pretty soon after.

09:58.432 --> 10:00.472
Certainly looks like motive.

10:05.639 --> 10:07.109
Huh.

10:07.106 --> 10:08.566
What can you tell me
about Nick Sand's death?

10:08.575 --> 10:11.005
Just that the bastard
finally got what he deserved.

10:11.011 --> 10:13.681
Okay. And why did
he deserve it?

10:13.680 --> 10:16.180
As soon as I took
the job at Wobble,

10:16.183 --> 10:18.083
