his personal mission

10:18.085 --> 10:20.045
to make my life hell.

10:20.053 --> 10:22.353
Sabotaging my work,
terrorizing me,

10:22.356 --> 10:24.516
making me the butt
of all of his jokes.

10:24.524 --> 10:26.864
Or the <i> balls,</i> in this case?

10:28.095 --> 10:29.385
That stupid video was

10:29.396 --> 10:31.356
