10:31.365 --> 10:34.265
Everyone saw it.
Everyone laughed at me!

10:34.267 --> 10:36.167
No one's laughing now, Tommy.

10:36.169 --> 10:38.769
So after everything
that happened, what,

10:38.772 --> 10:41.412
