what happened to him.

10:43.443 --> 10:45.883
Yeah, but you're not
answering the question.

10:47.814 --> 10:50.824
Did you kill Nick?

10:50.817 --> 10:52.677
I understand
punishment all too well, Tommy,

10:52.686 --> 10:56.286
and Nick deserved
to be punished.

10:56.289 --> 10:57.959
He did, didn't he?

10:57.958 --> 11:00.158
Mm. He took your
dignity, and so you had to

11:00.160 --> 11:01.490
take your revenge.

11:01.495 --> 11:05.025
There was no other way to get
your proverbial balls back.

11:05.032 --> 11:06.562
So tell me...

11:08.168 --> 11:09.728
