11:20.781 --> 11:23.421
Oh, come now, Detective.
He obviously wanted people

11:23.417 --> 11:24.947
to know that he got
his revenge.

11:24.951 --> 11:27.151
Now our would-be punisher's
brought to justice,

11:27.154 --> 11:30.464
and the field is mine again...

11:30.457 --> 11:33.187
What on earth is she doing here?

11:33.193 --> 11:34.693
