11:34.695 --> 11:36.755
The defense attorney
we saved, remember?

11:36.763 --> 11:39.503
She must be back here
defending some scumbag.

11:39.499 --> 11:42.599
But why are they
all being so... chummy?

11:42.602 --> 11:45.472
Well, she used to be
a cop, and, oh, yeah,

11:45.472 --> 11:47.142
'cause she's a knockout.

11:47.140 --> 11:49.470
Personally, I'm surprised
that you haven't tried...

11:49.476 --> 11:51.606
Pardon me, pardon me.
Excuse us.

11:51.611 --> 11:54.951
Charlotte, hello. Do you mind
if we have a quick word?

11:56.817 --> 11:59.617
What are you
doing here, Mother?

11:59.619 --> 12:01.149
