to yourself in a police station

12:20.941 --> 12:24.541
in this little... getup,
not a good idea.

12:24.544 --> 12:26.684
But I had to see
it for myself.

12:26.680 --> 12:29.180
My boy, working,
toiling,

12:29.182 --> 12:30.922
amidst humanity's muck.

12:30.917 --> 12:32.817
Well, I hope it's everything
you imagined and more.

12:32.819 --> 12:35.519
Now go see <i> Cabaret.</i> I'm sure
you'll find it riveting.

12:35.522 --> 12:36.792
I just don't understand.

12:36.790 --> 12:39.320
