enjoy exploring humanity?

12:44.865 --> 12:46.995
They eat, darling.

12:47.000 --> 12:48.130
All they do is eat.

12:48.135 --> 12:50.595
And then afterwards,
the food comes out changed

12:50.604 --> 12:53.614
and not for the better.

12:55.308 --> 12:56.878
Detective.

12:57.911 --> 12:59.141
I didn't realize

12:59.146 --> 13:01.006
you and Charlotte knew
each other so well.

13:01.014 --> 13:04.554
Oh, we do and we don't.
It's a long story, really.

13:04.551 --> 13:06.421
Right, shall we
go somewhere

13:06.419 --> 13:08.049
